name: Fit
description: Xeex ngir ay gëm-gëm, mën a jël ay matuwaay yu takku, te su ko jaree, fexe xeex ak doxalin ak xalaat yu fi nekkoon bu yàgg ba léegi.
questions: When did you last act courageously?
How hard is it for you to challenge the status quo, and why?
Where do you see real courage in others?
